des:
Hit Music for ALL of Northern Michigan. WKHQ-FM is a 100,000-watt radio station licensed to Charlevoix, Michigan, with studios located on U.S. 131 South Petoskey, Michigan and US 31 Acme, Michigan. The Top 40 (CHR) station, located at 105.9 MHz, is known to listeners as 106 KHQ, Northern Michigan's #1 Hit Music Channel.

106 KHQ is available to stream throughout Michigan and in most of the Midwest, but not all markets. If you hear no audio, it is because 106 KHQ is not available in that market. Our apologies for any inconvenience and thank you for listening to 106 KHQ.
